Description:
============
    Generates a new Hot ViewComponent at the passed path. If running under node,
    it'll also call the stimulus:manifest:update task to update the controllers/index.js.

Examples:
=========
    bin/rails generate hot_view_component Example

    creates: app/components/example_component.rb
    creates: app/components/example_component.html.erb
    creates: app/components/example_component.css
    creates: app/components/example_component_controller.js


    bin/rails generate stimulus nested/example

    creates: app/components/nested/example_component.rb
    creates: app/components/nested/example_component.html.erb
    creates: app/components/nested/example_component.css
    creates: app/components/nested/example_component_controller.js